instructions: Put the dinner plate on top and to the center of the table cloth
Put the salad plate on top of the dinner plate
Put the napkin on top of the salad plate
Put the wine glass on the top right corner of the table cloth
Put the water glass at a diagonal bottom right of the wine glass
Put the salad fork to the left of the dinner plate, on top of the table cloth
Put the dinner fork to the right of the salad fork
Put the dinner knife to the right on the dinner plate on top of the table cloth
Put the soup spoon next and to the right of the dinner knife
